				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				i am a ranger my self (right now using a oak recurve bow) the way the dmg and rng skill is,its much different than bows,like at level 10 with a 5 dmg weapon,you hit for 10 or even 11 sometimes,with a bow,lets say the dmg is 21,and rng is 125 (thats a oak recurve bow),with dmg 1 arrows,the bow will hit for a max of 22,2dmg arrows,hit for 23,and so on,same with range,it just adds it together,but im jus tsaying,the way it does damage with bows,is much different from swords and such (to bad it doesnt do bows like it does weapon),by the way,when grouped,like its posted above,always snare and get off one or two shots before the mob even gets to you,it really helps ,especially when your at a fast spawn camp,it will save healers and nukers alittle mana,and tanks alittle HP,its even beter if your a ranger and get a cirtical hit (with my bow i do 49dmg for each critical hit)
